text.tspan: Political rights vs. Mean years of schooling, 1975 to 2010
The vertical axis shows levels of democracy as measured by the Freedom House Political Rights Index. This index
ranges from 1 to 7, with 7 representing the least amount of political freedom and 1 the most freedom.
